:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB\" aria-label=\"种类 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>种类</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1360px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"       7974970\"\n        title=\"       7974970\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/adbd42f0eb6b7f5164690c433a844845/b5a09/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7974970.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/adbd42f0eb6b7f5164690c433a844845/f21e7/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7974970.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/adbd42f0eb6b7f5164690c433a844845/37523/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7974970.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/adbd42f0eb6b7f5164690c433a844845/b5a09/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7974970.png 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1362px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"      7977883\"\n        title=\"      7977883\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/14db048125edf76f47013602e1bc5822/d0c2f/%E7%82%B9%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7977883.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/14db048125edf76f47013602e1bc5822/f21e7/%E7%82%B9%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7977883.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/14db048125edf76f47013602e1bc5822/37523/%E7%82%B9%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7977883.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/14db048125edf76f47013602e1bc5822/d0c2f/%E7%82%B9%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F-7977883.png 1362w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1362px) 100vw, 1362px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1360px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"       \"\n        title=\"       \"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/332b0abffaa76e2414a18b7d09a98e83/b5a09/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/332b0abffaa76e2414a18b7d09a98e83/f21e7/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/332b0abffaa76e2414a18b7d09a98e83/37523/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/332b0abffaa76e2414a18b7d09a98e83/b5a09/%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%BE%BD%E6%A0%87.png 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">内容</th>\n<th align=\"left\">作用</th>\n<th align=\"left\">说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">数字徽标</td>\n<td align=\"left\">需要准确计数的场景</td>\n<td align=\"left\">一般出现在通知图标或头像的右上角，用于显示需要处理的消息条数； 由于界面显示空间有限，因此注意视场景和信息类型决定封顶数字显示</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">点徽标</td>\n<td align=\"left\">无需准确计数，仅做提醒的场景</td>\n<td align=\"left\">徽标中无具体数字显示，只出现红色小点，为了吸引用户注意，了解到有未读信息/未处理任务</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">自定义文本徽标</td>\n<td align=\"left\">满足多场景定制诉求</td>\n<td align=\"left\">可以根据场景展示数字以外的文本内容</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"颜色\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"颜色 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>颜色</h3>\n<h4 id=\"预设颜色\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%BE%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"预设颜色 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>预设颜色</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">描述</th>\n<th align=\"left\">背景色</th>\n<th align=\"left\">文本色</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">新功能点、消息通知的提示、默认⾊色值</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_LEGEND_RED_6</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_WHITE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">成功性质的提示</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T-COLOR-BRAND-GREEN-6</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_WHITE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">折扣信息、警告性质的提示</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_LEGEND_YELLOW_6</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_BLACK</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">进程中、主题⾊</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_BG_PRIMARY_1</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_WHITE</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"自定义颜色\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"自定义颜色 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>自定义颜色</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">描述</th>\n<th align=\"left\">背景色</th>\n<th align=\"left\">文本色</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">用在区别于预设颜色的徽标</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_BRAND_PURPLE_6</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_WHITE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">用在区别于预设颜色的徽标</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_BRAND_LIGHTBLUE_6</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_WHITE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">其他自定义颜色</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_BRAND_xxxxxx_6</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_TEXT_SYSTEM_WHITE</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>点徽标使用背景色。</li>\n<li>现有颜色无法满足需求时可使用其他自定义色值<code class=\"language-text\">T_COLOR_BRAND_xxxxx_6</code>，“xxxxx”代表颜色名。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"基本状态\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"基本状态 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本状态</h2>\n<p>预设多个颜色值，用作不同场景使用。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1360px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.944444444444443%; position: